================================================================================
Local MLX transcription lane (parakeet-mlx) — Apple Silicon, opt-in
================================================================================

This lane is installed on-demand, at the user's own machine, into a
dedicated local Python virtual environment (`<app-data>/mlx-venv`). None of
the packages or model weights below are bundled or redistributed inside the
JargonSlayer DMG/app bundle; they are downloaded directly by the user's
machine from PyPI and Hugging Face at install/first-run time.

